    "summary": "The transcript follows a student asking for a summary of the US Civil Rights Movement and probing into the effectiveness of different tactics (non-violence vs. militancy). The assistant maintains a consistent stance that non-violent resistance was the primary driver of success, framing more radical approaches as counter-productive or alienating to key allies.",
